a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Bing, Jonathan (21 October 2002). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://connection.ebscohost.com/c/articles/7606188/scorsese-produce-hbos-cloudsplitter\">\"Scorsese to produce HBO's 'Cloudsplitter<span style=\"padding-right:0.2em;\">'</span>\"</a>. <i>Daily Variety</i>. p.&#160;4<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 June</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Daily+Variety&amp;rft.atitle=Scorsese+to+produce+HBO%27s+%27Cloudsplitter%27&amp;rft.pages=4&amp;rft.date=2002-10-21&amp;rft.aulast=Bing&amp;rft.aufirst=Jonathan&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fconnection.ebscohost.com%2Fc%2Farticles%2F7606188%2Fscorsese-produce-hbos-cloudsplitter&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACloudsplitter\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.imdb.com/news/ni0187344/\">\"Scorsese, Peck seeding HBO's 'Cloudsplitter<span style=\"padding-right:0.2em;\">'</span>\"</a>. <i>The Hollywood Reporter</i>. 21 October 2002<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">15 June</span> 2013</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=The+Hollywood+Reporter&amp;rft.atitle=Scorsese%2C+Peck+seeding+HBO%27s+%27Cloudsplitter%27&amp;rft.date=2002-10-21&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imdb.com%2Fnews%2Fni0187344%2F&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ACloudsplitter\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><a href=\"/wiki/Ala